    • Method Detail

      • mergeAndStampPdfFiles

        public java.lang.String mergeAndStampPdfFiles(java.util.List<java.lang.String> files)
        This method get list of PDF-files names from JSON, gives this names to PDFService to do work. In case if one of files are not PDF-file, this file is skipped. List of not PDF files is printing in the result.
        Parameters:
        files - list of all PDF-files names.
        Returns:
        path to output file if work successfully done, or error cause if some errors occured. If there are no PDF files, returns "No PDF files detected".
